GUV.F.long_name: Graphisoft Park SE Real Estate Development European Company Limited
GUV.F.summary: Graphisoft Park SE Real Estate Development European Company Limited, through its subsidiaries, engages in real estate development and management activities in Hungary. It develops and operates Graphisoft Park, an office park that includes 61,000 square meters of office, laboratory, and educational space. The company is based in Budapest, Hungary.
